Description_lang: Every $t1 sec, gain a Null Barrier, absorbing ${$s1*(1+$@versadmg)} magic damage for $295842d.$?a295846[When Null Barrier expires, it implodes, dealing Shadow damage equal to the total amount absorbed, divided among all nearby enemies.][]

description_blz.en_US: Every 20 sec, gain a Null Barrier, absorbing 176 magic damage for 10 sec.
